content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.26 - Permission for jet-assisted take-offs required

State Regulations

Jet-assisted take-offs shall not be made at any air
terminal without obtaining permission and notifying the control tower in
advance. Notes
